Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, like, Kaleido \NStar is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star, please \Nkeep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can. 'Kay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's go! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have you ever made up your \Nmind about something?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Many things have happened in my 16-year life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've tried lots of hard things. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this time I'm earnest. I'm serious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I made up my mind in a super serious mode.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to take the challenge \Nfor everyone's future!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For everyone's future! For everyone's future!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dare mo sagashiteru yume wa kitto aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dokoka ni aru {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:01:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Negai ga itsuka kanau made hitori ja nai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saigo made yareru to ittetane {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kitto tsuyogatte itanda {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Itsudatte muchabakka de zutto karamawari de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dakedo anata dake ga soba ni ita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Daremo sagashiteru yume wa kitto aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arukidaseru {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koko kara nanika ga hajimaru {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shinjite itai {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:02:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mada minu hikari yakusoku \Nno basho e to tsuzuite yuku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Negai ga itsuka kanau made hitori ja naisa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:39.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Legendary Amazing Maneuver."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can see him too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about Fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the spirit of the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I expected, Layla's so calm. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So did I lose my mind, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's the one who lost his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Miss Layla,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you couldn't see him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla was chosen for the stage just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is proof that you can attempt \Nthe legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary great maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was tried once, a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, no one has successfully \Nperformed that maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One person was frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another tried it recklessly \Nand lost his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to attempt that maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will be the second pair \Nto try from Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to try the legendary great maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it needs two stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the two who \Ntried before and failed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One partner could not see me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the other one told me a lie and \Nmade him pretend he could see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Miss Layla can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please tell me, Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of maneuver is this \N"legendary great maneuver"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot tell you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until both of you are \Nqualified for that maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Qualified?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When is that? How can we be qualified?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it could be ten years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so mean. Just tell us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try that maneuver now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:04:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An avatar of Death...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid at least one of you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can do it if \Nit's with you, Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla, I will do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I not good enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we thought, the masked \Nstar was Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we have a time difference,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if she leaves London first \Nthing in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she can be here by noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try the legendary great \Nmaneuver with Miss Layla by any means.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary great maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I don't know what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I think I can do any kind of \Nmaneuver if I do it with Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, everyone, please come \Nclose and take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, the best show in history, \Nkinda, is going to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They found out that the \Nmasked star was Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd, you know, rather work with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I realized that I want \Nto appear on stage with Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's like, \Ntoo late to realize that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I feel the same, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The small audience must have something to do \Nwith the fact that we don't have Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it here, you can leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you are fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's, like, probably better for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:06:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she'll appear onscreen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is the movie shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished without a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to come back, Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to appear on stage with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only partner I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My current partner is Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may attempt the legendary \Ngreat maneuver with Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to attempt the legendary \Ngreat maneuver with Sora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way you can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you're going to do it, \Nthen I'll do it with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not qualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:07:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I saw the Kaleido \NStage for the first time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it was truly like a dream. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wished I could also appear on that stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After I started grade school, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and when I started learning \Ngymnastics, I thought it was fun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the first time in my life, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I learned how good applause made me feel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would practice very hard every day \Non a maneuver that I couldn't do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And when I was finally able to \Ndo it, when I received applause,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd feel so happy, I would tremble.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I got applause on \Nstage for the first time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it really made me happy. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I want to try \Neven more amazing maneuvers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I want to perform \Neven more amazing performances.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to show them. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want them to see it. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I want to perform on \Nthat stage with Miss Layla.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary great maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Kalos knows something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About people who took the challenge \Nbefore or something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't know if he's \Nwilling to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's never said anything \Nabout it to anybody before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the challengers are Sora and myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it's the two of \Nyou, it should be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you Kalos's contact information.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, damn! I wasn't watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, please do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you wait for a second, Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure work hard every day, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have no choice but to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I will be accepted \Nas Miss Layla's partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Layla Hamilton and Sora Naegino
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,return to their old home, Kaleido Stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to risk their lives attempting \Nthe legendary great maneuver."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It says next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that announcement about the legendary great \Nmaneuver being performed at Kaleido Stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tickets are already sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one performing in that show!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tickets are completely sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need them, I'll prepare \Nreserved seats for invited guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So just let me know the number of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:57.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know about the \Nlegendary great maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it from Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Miss Layla agreed to challenge the \Nlegendary great maneuver! Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri announced it without consulting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to make laughingstocks out of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just paying my respects to those who \Nare going to try a very difficult maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I decided to offer the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to back out of \Nthis, you should do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can quit anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All sold tickets are non-refundable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only people who lose \Nmoney are the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to cancel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have a condition of our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we succeed in performing \Nthe legendary great maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to return Kaleido Stage to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect you to perfect the \Nmaneuver without a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, no matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to perfect the legendary \Ngreat maneuver with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we're going to make sure to show that \Nmaneuver to the audience on this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but if we don't know \Nwhat kind of maneuver it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't know how we should practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos knows how we should practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss does?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used to watch the two \Nprevious challengers practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said if we are serious about doing \Nthis, come to the Grand Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he's going to give \Nus special training there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going, right, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really going to give \Nus Kaleido Stage back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For everyone's sake, I'm going to \Nperfect that maneuver by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm going to get back our Kaleido Stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Boss is coaching...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Jonathan. You cheer for her too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will go see your performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept hounding them for tickets, \Nand I already got some.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also participate \Nas your special trainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we all go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Boss knows what kind of maneuver \Nthat the legendary great maneuver is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finding out what it is without \Nbeing qualified means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to say "It's dangerous."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you kinda glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do my best to support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if the legendary great maneuver \Nis really that dangerous,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to lose you, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a hunch something bad will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I e-mailed everybody who used \Nto work for Kaleido Stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and asked them about the maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They told me that there were people who \Ntried that maneuver ten years ago, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder, could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, cook this one next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you taste this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... It, like, doesn't taste very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm not, like, really \Ngood at stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you finish that, \Ndo 100 one-arm chin-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So today's training is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, do 100 bicep curls \Nwith your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to cut it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, but I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep at it, on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A maneuver like that can't be possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to perfect the maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he said that he needed absolute confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is "he"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't just apply to those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It also applies to everybody around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can trust both Sora and Layla,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,never show your uncertainty or \Nbe soft on them until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cannot trust them, you \Nshould leave here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you will get in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't tell Sora what the \Nlegendary great maneuver is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But please bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to make sure to loosen \Nyour muscles very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, we'll have an interval by \Nletting you do some light workouts,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then the day after tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can endure this \Nkind of training till the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'm capable of doing \Nthe legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora is growing uncertain. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been doing the same \Ntraining for over a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no choice but to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Sora. Don't be so soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who told me you're going \Nto do the legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla, you've completed the first level.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to start training \Nusing a rope starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The iron ball hanging at the end of that wire
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,weighs almost the same as Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch this using only your \Nright arm and push it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't be Layla's partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can trust both Sora and Layla,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,never show your uncertainty or \Nbe soft on them until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me handle this training.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you capable of doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.66,0:21:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By any means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By any means, I'm going to do the legendary \Ngreat maneuver with Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you can do this, you can't \Nperfect the legendary great maneuver!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of maneuver is the \Nlegendary great maneuver?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without knowing what kind of maneuver it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can keep going till the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool, aren't you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When both of you are qualified \Nto do that maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.99,0:22:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:22:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm not good enough yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not? I'm not?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:36.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Kaleido Star"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you tell me with confidence \Nthat you're Layla's partner?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, I'm training so hard, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is ridiculous! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora is going to destroy herself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will not look away. I don't \Nwant to give up, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel like crying. I feel like running away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla, please say something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.05,0:22:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please! Please!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star, "The Amazing \NIntensive Training Continues."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream and \Non towards the sky...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.89,0:23:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boku wa koko ni iru sora to \Nmichi no aida de mukai kaze{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Soshite mae o muiteiru mou nido \Nto kanashimi ga furanai youni to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ano kabe o koete kokomade kitanda{\i0}
